Package: cbbdr
Title: Access Data from the College Basketball Data API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("John", "Edwards", , "edwards1860@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8533-7504"))
Description: Obtain data quickly and reliably from the College Basketball Data (CBBD) API. 
    You can safely and securely store your API key and use it to query the CBBD API, 
    grabbing data on men's college basketball and returning it in largely rectangular format.
URL: https://collegebasketballdata.com/
BugReports: https://github.com/john-b-edwards/cbbdr/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports: 
    cli,
    data.table,
    httr2,
    janitor,
    keyring,
    RcppSimdJson
